    org.apache.flink.api.java.ExecutionEnvironment.getNumberOfExecutionRetries()
    This method will be replaced by ExecutionEnvironment.getRestartStrategy(). The RestartStrategies.FixedDelayRestartStrategyConfiguration contains the number of execution retries.
    org.apache.flink.api.java.DataSet.print(String)
    Use DataSet.printOnTaskManager(String) instead.

    Use DataSet.printOnTaskManager(String) instead, othe PrintingOutputFormat instead.

    Please use TwoInputUdfOperator.returns(Class) or TwoInputUdfOperator.returns(TypeHint) instead.
    org.apache.flink.api.java.operators.SingleInputUdfOperator.returns(String)
    Please use SingleInputUdfOperator.returns(Class) or SingleInputUdfOperator.returns(TypeHint) instead.
    org.apache.flink.api.java.ExecutionEnvironment.setNumberOfExecutionRetries(int)
    This method will be replaced by ExecutionEnvironment.setRestartStrategy(org.apache.flink.api.common.restartstrategy.RestartStrategies.RestartStrategyConfiguration). The RestartStrategies.FixedDelayRestartStrategyConfiguration contains the number of execution retries.
